article_title: Choptank Community Health to bring dental care to St. Michaels
article_text:
Easton, MD (21601)

Today

Partly cloudy skies. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High around 85F. Winds SSW at 10 to 15 mph..

Tonight

A few clouds. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low 66F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph.

og.description: ST. MICHAELS — In September, Choptank Community Health System announced plans to open a new dental center at its Bay Hundred location in St. Michaels.
